{"tid":1612892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃大仙警加班工作染感冒　寓所猝死","createTime":"2019-10-02T11:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T00:19:23.000Z","uid":176074,"like":136,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"1c70dc11410f4b1dc53cfce83534349f8537e6ff","tid":1612892,"uid":176074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:29:29.000Z","msg":"反修例示威集會不斷已逾3個月，警員長期超時工作疲於奔命。昨日(30日)，一名駐守黃大仙警區特遣隊的49歲「老差骨」被發現在寓所內猝死。據了解，死者生前人稱「輝哥」，居於油塘高翔苑的紀律部隊宿舍，在近月的遊行示威中時常加班當值逾10小時，惟於近日終染上感冒。<br />\n死者前晚疑食藥進睡後，至昨日無故缺勤，又失去聯絡，有同袍上門了解時始發現他已陷入昏迷，救護員趕至經檢驗後證實他已氣絕身亡，警方隨即聯絡死者家屬並協助辦理後事。有認識死者的同袍慨嘆指，死者工作一直都盡心盡力，是一位值得尊敬的同僚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191001/mobile/bkn-20191001125558589-1001_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191001%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191001125558589-1001_00822_001.html&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=d25a64d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191001/mobile/bkn-20191001125558589-1001_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e9a8b649c4c3432a29152c47415ffb1d424f022e","tid":1612892,"uid":33939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:30:38.000Z","msg":"係咪應該一齊去哀悼？"},{"pid":"2471296cdf8ece8a2ffdd2a9d4b792798ac96102","tid":1612892,"uid":293254,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:30:45.000Z","msg":"肯定比共狗滅口"},{"pid":"414701740c90700a1203ec8aaa31d8c9664ab5f5","tid":1612892,"uid":267277,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:30:51.000Z","msg":"報應來得太快就像龍卷風"},{"pid":"c08cced50272746a5d30ff786281087cf67f3fc1","tid":1612892,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:31:07.000Z","msg":"去開party?"},{"pid":"9c56fbaa7e6f22ff49b3e077095a172f36638c86","tid":1612892,"uid":122202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:32:51.000Z","msg":"我地冇左十幾廿個手足 死一隻黑狗又何足惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.g